abstract: College Football Top 25 Roundup; Oklahoma defeats Oklahoma State, 58-23; other college football scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Baker Mayfield threw two touchdown passes and ran for another score, and No. 5 Oklahoma beat No. 9 Oklahoma State, 58-23, on the road.

headline.main: Oklahoma Makes Its Playoff Case by Pounding Oklahoma State
